                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/Grades/all" class="sidebar-item active flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100">
                        <div class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
